These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-4-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, coffee, water
There 3 different types of food: banana, lemon, blueberry
The people have 3 different jobs:  teacher, nurse, chef
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: spy, sports, epic
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: rock, techno, hip-hop
There are 3 different nationalities: nigerian, malaysian, australian
3 different pets are kept: mouse, goat, horse
 1. the fan of rock is the person eating lemon##1
 2. the nurse is on the left or right of the australian##3
 3. the person watching sports movies is on the left or right of the owner of the horse##3
 4. the teacher is the australian##1
 5. the owner of the mouse is between the person eating blueberry and the person drinking water##2
 6. the person drinking coffee is in an odd position##4
 7. the person eating blueberry is on the left or right of the malaysian##3
 8. the person watching epic movies is on the far right##1
 9. the person eating lemon is between the nigerian and the fan of techno##2
10. the person watching sports movies is the nurse##1
11. the owner of the mouse is between the person watching epic movies and the australian##2
12. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
13. the owner of the horse is the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |         3          |
| Beverage      | water | sprite     | coffee      |
| Food          | banana | lemon | blueberry               |
| Job           | teacher   | nurse   | chef |
| Movie-Genre   | spy  | sports | epic           |
| Music-Genre   | techno  | rock   | hip-hop               |
| Nationality   | australian  | malaysian   | nigerian           |
| Pet           | goat   | mouse      | horse              |

