.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-4-2::.
There 3 different types of food: avocado, pumpkin, apricot
The people have 3 different hobbies: skydiving, reading, fishing
The people have 3 different jobs:  doctor, coach, mechanic
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: reggae, electronic, classical
There are 3 different nationalities: french, german, american
3 different pets are kept: goat, fish, rabbit
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, badminton, water-polo
 1. the coach is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is fishing##3
 2. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
 3. the owner of the rabbit is in an odd position##4
 4. the doctor is the owner of the rabbit##1
 5. the person who's sport is water-polo is the german##1
 6. the french is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
 7. the person who's sport is rowing is the person eating avocado##1
 8. the fan of classical is in the middle##1
 9. the person eating avocado is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
10. the german is the doctor##1
11. the person who's hobby is reading is the american##1
12. the doctor is on the left or right of the mechanic##3
13. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the far right##1
14. the german is in an odd position##4
15. the owner of the goat is the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |
| Food          | pumpkin     | avocado      | apricot      |
| Hobby         | reading    | fishing  | skydiving |
| Job           | coach | mechanic   | doctor |
| Music-Genre   | electronic     | classical    | reggae      |
| Nationality   | american  | french | german    |
| Pet           | fish    | goat       | rabbit     |
| Sport         | badminton  | rowing   | water-polo   |

