There are 3 different nationalities: british, turkish, thai
3 different pets are kept: hamster, dog, rabbit
The people use 3 different means of transport: tram, helicopter, skateboard
 1. the fan of dubstep is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person drinking 7up is in an even position##4
 3. the thai is on the far right##1
 4. the person eating banana is the person driving the skateboard##1
 5. the fan of rock is on the far right##1
 6. the fan of funk is between the british and the firefighter##2
 7. the person eating eggplant is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
 8. the person eating banana is on the left or right of the turkish##3
 9. the owner of the dog is on the far left##1
10. the person drinking coffee is the owner of the hamster##1
11. the accountant is on the left of the doctor##1
12. the person driving the tram is on the far left##1
13. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person driving the tram##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |        3        |
| Beverage      | iced-tea    | 7up     | coffee        |
| Food          | grapes    | eggplant   | banana      |
| Job           | accountant | doctor | firefighter |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep  | funk      | rock           |
| Nationality   | british   | turkish | thai        |
| Pet           | dog     | rabbit     | hamster             |
