 1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far right##1
 2. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the designer##1
 3. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the fan of folk##1
 4. the fan of reggae is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is reading##3
 5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left or right of the person who's sport is climbing##3
 6. the fan of folk is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the chef is the person watching mystery movies##1
 8. the person watching satire movies is the person driving the boat##1
 9. the person driving the bike is in an even position##4
10. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
11. the polish is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
12. the person who's sport is climbing is the designer##1
13. the spanish is the fan of soul##1

.:: Answer ::.
