 1. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the person who's sport is climbing##3
 2. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the bartender##3
 3. the fan of gospel is between the person who's sport is rugby and the person who's hobby is cooking##2
 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the owner of the fish##1
 5. the pakistani is on the far left##1
 6. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the bartender##1
 7. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 8. the fan of electronic is on the left or right of the canadian##3
 9. the accountant is on the left of the person drinking water##1
10. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is in an even position##4
11. the person drinking water is on the left of the fan of electronic##1

.:: Answer ::.
