 4. the manager is the person watching scientific movies##1
 5. the person who's sport is parkour is the dancer##1
 6. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far right##1
 7. the pakistani is on the left or right of the person eating onion##3
 8. the person who's sport is surfing is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the italian is between the person eating lime and the manager##2
10. the pakistani is on the far left or far right##3
11. the person driving the motorbike is the person driving the motorbike##1
12. the person who's sport is cricket is in an odd position##4
13. the person drinking soy-milk is the person driving the motorbike##1
14. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the far left or far right##3
15. the person eating onion is on the left or right of the person eating kale##3

