.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-4-16::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: woodworking, gardening, drawing
The people have 3 different jobs:  librarian, dressmaker, fisherman
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: house, punk, funk
There are 3 different nationalities: italian, british, american
3 different pets are kept: frog, bird, hedgehog
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: parkour, climbing, water-polo
The people use 3 different means of transport: tram, motorbike, roller
 1. the person who's sport is parkour is on the far left##1
 2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far left##1
 3. the fan of funk is in an even position##4
 4. the owner of the bird is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the british is on the right of the fisherman##1
 6. the fan of funk is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 7. the person driving the tram is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 8. the american is on the far left##1
 9. the person driving the roller is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
10. the person who's hobby is drawing is the italian##1
11. the librarian is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
12. the person who's hobby is gardening is between the fan of punk and the dressmaker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2      |       3       |
| Hobby         | woodworking     | gardening      | drawing  |
| Job           | fisherman | librarian   | dressmaker      |
| Music-Genre   | punk         | funk       | house          |
| Nationality   | american     | british     | italian    |
| Pet           | hedgehog         | frog        | bird    |
| Sport         | parkour        | water-polo | climbing |
| Transport     | roller          | tram       | motorbike          |

