.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-4-17::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, sprite, milk
There 3 different types of food: mango, blueberry, pineapple
The people have 3 different hobbies: filmmaking, chess, rock-climbing
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, fantasy, martial-arts
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: techno, r&b, blues
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, hamster, dog
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, ship, roller
 1. the person watching martial-arts movies is the fan of blues##1
 2. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person driving the bike##1
 3. the owner of the dog is the person watching fantasy movies##1
 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the fan of techno##1
 5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person eating blueberry##1
 7. the person driving the ship is in an even position##4
 8. the fan of blues is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the dog is in the middle##1
10. the person eating blueberry is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
11. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
12. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
13. the fan of techno is on the far left or far right##3
14. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the fan of r&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
