.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-4-19::.
There 3 different types of food: plum, strawberry, corn
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, scientist, librarian
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: time-travel, fantasy, superhero
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: pop, soul, trance
3 different pets are kept: rat, horse, hedgehog
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: basketball, surfing, snowboarding
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, boat, snowmobile
 1. the person driving the boat is the person who's sport is surfing##1
 2. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 3. the scientist is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
 4. the scientist is on the far left##1
 5. the owner of the hedgehog is the person eating corn##1
 6. the person watching time-travel movies is in an odd position##4
 7. the owner of the horse is in an odd position##4
 8. the accountant is on the right of the fan of soul##1
 9. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
10. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the person eating corn##1
11. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the fan of pop##1
12. the person watching superhero movies is on the left or right of the fan of pop##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |    3     |
| Food          | corn    | strawberry       | plum   |
| Job           | scientist    | accountant | librarian   |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | fantasy         | time-travel   |
| Music-Genre   | soul    | pop      | trance   |
| Pet           | hedgehog     | rat   | horse     |
| Sport         | snowboarding   | surfing       | basketball |
| Transport     | helicopter      | boat       | snowmobile      |

