.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-4-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, tea, 7up
There 3 different types of food: grapes, watermelon, blueberry
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: rock, punk, metal
There are 3 different nationalities: mexican, colombian, dutch
3 different pets are kept: pony, goat, guinea-pig
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, weightlifting, cricket
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, helicopter, tram
 1. the mexican is in an odd position##4
 2. the owner of the pony is in an even position##4
 3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3
 4. the person drinking tea is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person drinking coffee##2
 5. the mexican is on the left of the person eating blueberry##1
 6. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's sport is weightlifting is between the colombian and the person driving the tram##2
 8. the fan of metal is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
 9. the person who's sport is lacrosse is in an odd position##4
10. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3
11. the fan of punk is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
12. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person eating watermelon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3     |
| Beverage      | 7up       | tea      | coffee    |
| Food          | grapes | blueberry     | watermelon    |
| Music-Genre   | rock    | metal        | punk     |
| Nationality   | mexican  | dutch       | colombian |
| Pet           | goat        | pony          | guinea-pig  |
| Sport         | cricket     | weightlifting | lacrosse   |
| Transport     | tram        | helicopter          | motorbike |

 